metadata.name: Lonely Robot Girl # 1
metadata.description: She cannot speak her words and no one understands her feelings. Her inner core (heart) is exploding and her skin is burnt and disintegrating due to the intense heat. Maybe the time has come for him to fall into eternal sleep.Another piece 1/1 of the gif collection called "Lonely Robot Girl" is now available.This is a raw image that has been edited once and a gif animation again.
